OL,6,FA criminal gang who kidnapped and
OL,7,Fstole hundreds of thousands of pounds
OL,8,Ffrom a "vulnerable" man has been
OL,9,Fjailed for a total of 76 years.
OL,11,FThe plot began to unravel when in
OL,12,FDecember 2023 police were called to a
OL,13,Fflat in Irlam, Salford, after there
OL,14,Fwas an anonymous report of concern for
OL,15,Fwelfare.
OL,17,FInside they found a man who said he
OL,18,Fhad been forced to go to the flat with
OL,19,Fa bag over his head, and who asked
OL,20,Fthem to take him away with them.
