OL,6,FThe victim said that he had been
OL,7,Fassaulted and tied up, and police
OL,8,Fofficers found bindings on the bed,
OL,9,Fburn marks and bruises on his body
OL,10,Fwhere he had been tortured.
OL,12,FAs the investigation into the man's
OL,13,Fclaims got underway detectives
OL,14,Fdiscovered that he had come into
OL,15,Fhundreds of thousands of pounds of
OL,16,Fcryptocurrency which the gang had been
OL,17,Fextorting from him for almost a year.
