OL,6,FAt the flat police uncovered an
OL,7,Farsenal of weapons including guns and
OL,8,Fammunition, a machete and a baseball
OL,9,Fbat, together with evidence pointing
OL,10,Fat two gang members.
OL,12,FDetectives discovered that the gang
OL,13,Fhad repeatedly terrorised the victim,
OL,14,Fcalling at his home to threaten him
OL,15,Fand also kidnapping him and taking him
OL,16,Fto the Cadishead area where he was
OL,17,Fheld overnight, beaten up and
OL,18,Fthreatened with being killed if he did
OL,19,Fnot pay up.
