OL,6,FThey seven gang members are now
OL,7,Fbeginning jail sentences totalling 76
OL,8,Fyears, two of them facing 20 years in
OL,9,Fjail for a variety of offences ranging
OL,10,Ffrom kidnapping, robbery, possessing a
OL,11,Ffirearm and false imprisonment.
OL,13,FInvestigating officer, Detective
OL,14,FSergeant Stephanie Bowling, said:
OL,15,F"This was a challenging investigation
OL,16,Fwhich has thankfully resulted in these
OL,17,Fdangerous offenders being removed from
OL,18,Fthe streets for a significant amount
OL,19,Fof time.
